__e: Reminds me of a cowpuncher who went to wash his feet one spring... and found he had two pairs of socks on he didn't know he had.
I'm sure he puts his ear buds in one at a time, just like the rest of us.
Really? So how come you're not wearing any socks?
- I don't eat socks. And I don't appreciate being tied up.
- Suppose I get tired of coffee, I'm not wounded or sick, I give up smoking, have only one pair of socks, and roll up my robe myself. What then?
What is it you want? A husband who will darn your socks? - Sounds interesting.
